1.title: Monsters in My Head
1.plot: Kimberley is terrorized by a shadow demon, Alexi calls in a demonologist to exorcise a malign spirit and Darryl takes a terrifying journey to the depths of hell.

2.title: Sleeping with the Devil
2.plot: Every night, Korey wakes up with a demon sitting on her. Carey is being terrorized by the ghost of a Native American warrior and Craig is convinced his body has been invaded by an alien.

3.title: Animal Demons
3.plot: Becky's life has been destroyed by mysterious bugs, Heather is traumatized by ants, spiders and moose. Emilio is haunted by hallucinations that turn members of his family into ghoulish monsters.
